<F P=101> Cuba </F>
<H3> <TI>   Havana Water Distribution Affected By Repairs </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Havana Water Distribution Affected By Repairs </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL0905215194 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1954 GMT 
9 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0905215194 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Reloj Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Havana City aqueduct has announced that from 
9-13 May, the water supply in several Havana municipalities will 
be affected. Some zones of the San Miguel del Padron 
Municipality will be affected due to repair work on the supply 
wells in the [word indistinct] area. Other zones affected are: 
Reparto Veracruz, San Matias, Diezmero, Caballo Blanco, the 
higher part of La Rosita, Alturas de Luyano, and Las Delicias. 
The management of the Havana City aqueduct apologizes for any 
inconvenience. 

</TEXT>

