<H3> <TI>   Judge Confirms Arrest of Nazi Officer </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Judge Confirms Arrest of Nazi Officer </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY1005150494 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 
1209 GMT 10 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY1005150494 </F>
<F P=104>  Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
