  [Text] Buenos Aires, 10 May (NA) -- Judge Leonidas Moldes, 
who is hearing the case of former Nazi Captain Erich Priebke, 
reported this morning that the latter will make a deposition 
before the San Carlos de Bariloche federal courts in the next 
few hours. 
  Judge Moldes confirmed that the former Nazi officer was 
arrested at Bariloche Clinic, which is owned by Priebke, 
yesterday evening. He made it clear that "so far no formal 
extradition request" has been filed by the Italian courts. 

